subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Eighth-seeded Kentucky ended Wichita State’s unbeaten season, rallying in the second half and prevailing when Fred VanVleet missed a 3-point shot at the buzzer.
